  source novel kubrick based his adapted screenplay on william makepeace thackeray 's the luck of barry lyndon ( republished as the novel memoirs of barry lyndon , esq . ) , a picaresque tale written and published in serial form in 1844 .

pen names : this " vanity fair " author liked to assume the name george savage fitz - boodle , listing him as the editor of " barry lyndon "

